OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFeeling seasonally warm and in
OL,6,Fthe northern end of the Great Glen
OL,7,Fvery warm. Most in east staying dry
OL,8,Fwith occasional brighter spells, but
OL,9,Fsome patchy rain across the west,
OL,10,Fturning heavier towards early evening.
OL,11,FSoutheast winds fresh around coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud thickening to bring
OL,14,Fperiods of rain, with some heavier
OL,15,Foutbreaks late evening and during the
OL,16,Fearly hours of Wednesday, before
OL,17,Fturning patchy towards dawn. Southerly
OL,18,Fcoastal winds initially fresh.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
