OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FTemperatures still up on
OL,6,Fseasonally averages, but significantly
OL,7,Fcooler than today. Rather cloudy
OL,8,Fmorning with some patchy light rain,
OL,9,Ffocused in the west. Mainly dry for
OL,10,Fafternoon with brighter spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fearly Thursday, clearing to frequent
OL,14,Fshowers for the afternoon. Friday wet
OL,15,Fand windy with best of shelter towards
OL,16,FInverness. Blustery showers Saturday,
OL,17,Fheavier and more frequent in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
